@startuml phase2_discovery
' Sequence diagram: Groq receives profile.json → suggests roles → user selects role + location + radius → Apify scrapes LinkedIn jobs → results written to targets.json → UI displays count → user reviews and de-selects

actor User
participant "Discovery UI" as UI
participant "Discovery Service" as Service
participant "Groq Service" as Groq
participant "Apify Service" as Apify
database "JSON Store" as Store

User -> UI : Enter Discovery Phase
UI -> Service : get_role_suggestions()
Service -> Store : read("profile.json")
Store --> Service : profile_data
Service -> Groq : suggest_roles(profile_data)
Groq --> Service : list_of_roles
Service --> UI : roles
UI -> User : Show suggestions

User -> UI : Select role, location, radius
UI -> Service : start_discovery(role, loc, rad)
Service -> Apify : run_linkedin_jobs_scraper(role, loc, rad)
Apify --> Service : raw_jobs_list
Service -> Store : write("targets.json", jobs_list)
Store --> Service : success
Service --> UI : job_count
UI -> User : Display "Found {N} companies"

User -> UI : Review and de-select targets
UI -> Service : finalize_targets(selected_ids)
Service -> Store : update_targets(selected_ids)
Store --> Service : success
@enduml
